ăn nhân thi - 御制文人詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-wQmKl2dTgK9nLW9ChBRQEA">Tây giang nguyệt kỳ 3 - 西江月其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-L%E1%BB%87nh-Do/Th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-qu%E1%BA%A3i-h%C3%BAc/poem-LwzM2QiuwfkF51soXinEWA">Thành kỳ quải húc - 城旗掛旭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-L%E1%BB%87nh-Do/author-nGqxPF4ZCL72MRJfhbE9-w">Đỗ Lệnh Do</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%B1-Tri%E1%BB%87t-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Th%E1%BA%A5t-ng%C6%B0u/poem-Cc0QauDIW2DIsSizuPvl-A">Thất ngưu - 失牛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%B1-Tri%E1%BB%87t-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-hLieU30kQX-lghGB7hIRaQ">Cự Triệt thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-kinh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Gw3OZ5FgtrH189qxcANZuQ">Thu kinh kỳ 2 - 收京其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
